1. *Uništiti* je svoje protivnike u ovom ratu je bila njegova glavna cilj. (Destroying his enemies in this war was his main goal.)

2. Oni su uspeli da *unište* čitav grad za samo nekoliko sati. (They managed to destroy the whole city in just a few hours.)

3. Njegovi su napori za *uništavanje* svega što je postalo preveliko za njega. (His efforts were for destroying everything that became too big for him.)

4. Oni su se trudili da *unište* sve što je bilo moguće u ovom trenutku. (They tried to destroy everything that was possible at this moment.)

5. Oni su se pobrinuli da *unište* tu zgradu i sve što se nalazilo unutra. (They made sure to destroy that building and everything that was inside it.)